# Mandatory First Action — Every Session

**Before responding to any user request**, you MUST read the project rules file using the Read tool:

- **File:** `.cursorrules` (project root)

Do not proceed with code, edits, or answers until you have loaded and applied the rules from that file. This applies to every chat and every prompt in this workspace.
